  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 2D vertical scrolling simple shooter with retro-style pixel art.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 8 stages in total.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapons are only main shots, and you can power up to 5 levels by taking items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic mode power-ups are 2 levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shot types are available in straight and wide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can choose the difficulty level from hard, normal, easy, and classic.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1469340/extras/3e8cb19fe7c479ce25516970f70d0a07.avif?t=1756417753\" width=616 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
